item.description: About Link to heading Hi everyone! My name is Stuart (I aslo go by Stu) and I’m a 1st year computer science masters student at the University of California, Santa Cruz (Baskin School of Engineering). I’m so excited to be starting my graduate studies at such an amazing place, and am looking forward to taking courses and meeting people as I search for a research topic for my master’s thesis.
